    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And Simon, and they that were with him,.... Peter, and his brother Andrew, together with James and John, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "followed after him; some time after he was gone; for he privately withdrew from them, so that they might not be aware when he went, nor apprized of his departure, for some considerable time; which when they were, they set out, in diligent search, and eager pursuit after him, until they found him. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "followed after him; some time after he was gone; for he privately withdrew from them, so that they might not be aware when he went, nor apprized of his departure, for some considerable time; which when they were, they set out, in diligent search, and eager pursuit after him, until they found him. ",
